        "content_en": "Period = principal energy level. Group = same number of valence electrons. Periodic trends: atomic radius (increases down and left), ionization energy (increases up and right), electronegativity (increases up and right), electron affinity.",
        "content_zh": "周期 = 主能级。族 = 相同价电子数。周期性趋势：原子半径（向下和向左增大），电离能（向上和向右增大），电负性（向上和向右增大），电子亲和能。"
      }
