        "content_en": "Relative atomic mass: average mass of an element's atoms relative to 1/12 mass of carbon-12. Molecular mass: sum of atomic masses in a molecule. Atomic mass unit (amu): 1/12 mass of ¹²C atom = 1.66×10⁻²⁴ g.",
