        "content_en": "Alkanes (CₙH₂ₙ₊₂): only single bonds (saturated). Alkenes (CₙH₂ₙ): one double bond. Alkynes (CₙH₂ₙ₋₂): one triple bond. Aromatic hydrocarbons: e.g., benzene C₆H₆ (unsaturated ring with special stability from resonance).",
        "content_zh": "烷烃（CₙH₂ₙ₊₂）：只有单键（饱和）。烯烃（CₙH₂ₙ）：一个双键。炔烃（CₙH₂ₙ₋₂）：一个三键。芳香烃：如苯C₆H₆（具有共振稳定性的不饱和环）。"
      },
