        "content_en": "Addition: adding a molecule to a double/triple bond (e.g., Br₂ to alkene). Substitution: replacing an atom/group with another (e.g., alkane halogenation). Elimination: removing a small molecule to form a multiple bond (e.g., dehydration of alcohol to alkene). Polymerization: joining small units (monomers) to form a polymer.",
        "content_zh": "加成：将分子添加到双键/三键上（如Br₂加至烯烃）。取代：用另一个原子/基团替换一个原子/基团（如烷烃卤化）。消除：移除一个小分子形成多重键（如醇脱水生成烯烃）。聚合：小单元（单体）结合形成聚合物。"
      },
