        "content_en": "Identify the longest continuous carbon chain. Number the chain from the end nearest the functional group or substituent. Name substituents (alkyl groups: methyl, ethyl...) in alphabetical order. Specify position numbers for substituents or multiple bonds.",
        "content_zh": "确定最长的连续碳链。从最靠近官能团或取代基的一端开始编号。按字母顺序命名取代基（烷基：甲基、乙基...）。指定取代基或多键的位置编号。"
