        "content_en": "Plane areas: square s², rectangle L×W, triangle ½×b×h, circle πr², parallelogram b×h, trapezoid ½(a+b)×h. Solid volumes: cube s³, rectangular prism L×W×H, sphere ⁴⁄₃πr³, cylinder πr²h, cone ⅓πr²h, pyramid ⅓×base area×height. Surface area: sphere 4πr², cylinder 2πrh+2πr², cone πrl+πr² (l = slant height).",
        "content_zh": "常见面积公式：三角形 A = ½×底×高；矩形 A = 长×宽；圆 A = πr²；梯形 A = ½×(上底+下底)×高。常见体积公式：球 V = ⁴⁄₃πr³；圆柱 V = πr²h；圆锥 V = ⅓πr²h；长方体 V = 长×宽×高。注意区分二维面积和三维体积公式。"
      },
      {
