        "content_en": "Random variable X: function from sample space to real numbers. Discrete distribution: PMF P(X=x). Binomial: X ~ B(n,p), P(X=k)=C(n,k)pᵏ(1−p)ⁿ⁻ᵏ, E(X)=np, Var(X)=np(1−p). Poisson: X~P(λ), P(X=k)=e⁻λλᵏ/k!, E(X)=λ, Var(X)=λ. Normal (Gaussian): bell curve, X~N(μ,σ²), 68-95-99.7 rule.",
        "content_zh": "离散分布：二项分布 X ~ B(n,p)，P(X=k) = C(n,k)pᵗ(1−p)ⁿ⁻ᵗ。均值 = np，方差 = np(1−p)。泊松分布 X ~ P(λ)，P(X=k) = e⁻λ λᵗ/k!。连续分布：正态分布 X ~ N(μ,σ²)，钟形曲线，68-95-99.7 法则。标准正态分布 Z = (X−μ)/σ。贝叶斯定理：P(A|B) = P(B|A)P(A)/P(B)。"
